am confirmed Conner's death toThe Independent.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_water_polo_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US Water Polo team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_water_polo_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_water_polo_team\"}, {\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999506599, \"rank\": 4.653620664339204e-11, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was the 26-year-old sister of Steffens' husband Bobby Conner.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The family has not released details of her cause of death.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was so excited for the Olympic Games,\\\" Steffens told The Associated Press on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999970832035862, \"rank\": 2.9163787945079967e-06, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are really close.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's the light of the world.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She just brings so much joy to everyone.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She always brings people together.\\\"\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conner had made clock necklaces for members of the women's water polo team and rapper Flavor Flav, the team's hype man.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.433034320987269e-31, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steffens said her team has been rallying behind her in the aftermath of her loss.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been obviously really struggling, and my husband as well, and his entire family.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, it's a nightmare, and it's completely shocking.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think just feeling her spirit here is, like I said, it's amazing.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I hope that we can make her proud every single day,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete managed to score two goals while playing against Greece on Saturday.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7358829748353017, \"rank\": 0.35889851748757345, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US won 15 to 6.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1865, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.